commit.message:
cpuinfo.c (enum vendor_signatures): Remove.

	* config/i386/cpuinfo.c (enum vendor_signatures): Remove.
	(__cpu_indicator_init): Use signature_INTEL_ebx and signature_AMD_ebx
	from cpuid.h to check vendor signatures.
